<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="referrer" content="no-referrer">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'self' data: blob:; script-src 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob:; connect-src https://api.openai.com; font-src 'self' data:; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'; form-action 'none'">
  <title>R&amp;D Review Studio v-10</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: light;
      --bg: #f3f6fa;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-2: #f7f9fc;
      --ink: #172033;
      --muted: #667085;
      --line: #dce3ed;
      --navy: #14375f;
      --blue: #2463a8;
      --blue-soft: #e8f1fb;
      --green: #13795b;
      --green-soft: #e8f6f0;
      --amber: #a15c00;
      --amber-soft: #fff4df;
      --red: #b42318;
      --red-soft: #ffebe9;
      --violet: #6941c6;
      --violet-soft: #f1edff;
      --shadow: 0 12px 34px rgba(20, 55, 95, 0.08);
      --radius: 18px;
      --radius-sm: 11px;
      --max: 1440px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    .sr-only { position:absolute !important; width:1px !important; height:1px !important; padding:0 !important; margin:-1px !important; overflow:hidden !important; clip:rect(0,0,0,0) !important; white-space:nowrap !important; border:0 !important; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    button, input, select, textarea { font: inherit; }
    button { cursor: pointer; }
    button:disabled { cursor: not-allowed; opacity: .55; }
    :focus-visible { outline: 3px solid rgba(36, 99, 168, .25); outline-offset: 2px; }
    .hidden { display: none !important; }
    .app-shell { min-height: 100vh; }
    .topbar {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(20,55,95,.05);
    }
    .topbar-inner {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      min-height: 74px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .brand-logo { display:block; width:260px; max-width:44vw; height:auto; }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #5cb4ff, #2f72c0);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
    }
    .brand-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 750; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
    .brand-sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .session-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 7px 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .session-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #8ea5bd; }
    .session-badge.connected .session-dot { background: #58d4a8; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(88,212,168,.14); }
    .workflow {
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .workflow-inner {
      width: min(920px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      padding: 18px 0;
    }
    .workflow-step {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 650;
    }
    .workflow-step:not(:last-child)::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      right: -16%;
      width: 32%;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--line);
    }
    .step-number {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #fff;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .workflow-step.active { color: var(--blue); }
    .workflow-step.active .step-number { background: var(--blue); color: #fff; border-color: var(--blue); }
    .workflow-step.done { color: var(--green); }
    .workflow-step.done .step-number { background: var(--green-soft); color: var(--green); border-color: #a8d7c7; }
    main {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 34px 0 64px;
    }
    .view-head { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .intro-hero { display:grid; grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.35fr) minmax(300px,.65fr); gap:22px; align-items:stretch; margin-bottom:24px; }
    .intro-copy { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#174f99,#2676c5); color:#fff; border-radius:18px; padding:26px 28px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
    .intro-copy .eyebrow { color:#cfe6ff; }
    .intro-copy h1 { max-width:850px; }
    .intro-copy p { margin:0; color:#e7f2ff; max-width:900px; }
    .intro-flow { display:grid; gap:9px; }
    .intro-step { display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; align-items:center; gap:11px; background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:13px; padding:12px 14px; }
    .intro-step strong { display:block; font-size:13px; }
    .intro-step span:last-child { color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; }
    .intro-step-number { width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:9px; display:grid; place-items:center; background:var(--blue-soft); color:var(--blue); font-weight:800; font-size:12px; }
    .intro-note { grid-column:1/-1; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:7px; margin-top:2px; }
    .intro-chip { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; padding:6px 9px; background:#eef4fb; border:1px solid #d7e3f0; border-radius:999px; color:#40536c; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; }
    .eyebrow { color: var(--blue); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    h1, h2, h3, p { margin-top: 0; }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 7px; font-size: clamp(25px, 3vw, 36px); letter-spacing: -.04em; line-height: 1.2; }
    h2 { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: -.025em; }
    h3 { margin-bottom: 7px; font-size: 15px; }
    .lead { margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--muted); max-width: 900px; }
    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
    .grid-2 > *, .grid-3 > * { min-width: 0; }
    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .card + .card, .stack > * + * { margin-top: 20px; }
    .card-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .card-head p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 13px; }
    .section-number {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 11px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: var(--blue-soft);
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .head-copy { display: flex; gap: 13px; }
    .notice {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      background: var(--amber-soft);
      color: #6f4305;
      border: 1px solid #f3d49c;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .notice strong { color: #553100; }
    .notice-icon { font-weight: 900; flex: 0 0 auto; }
    label, legend { font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; }
    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 7px; }
    .field small, .helper { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    input[type="text"], input[type="password"], input[type="date"], select, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      min-height: 44px;
    }
    textarea { min-height: 92px; resize: vertical; }
    .input-with-action { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 8px; }
    .btn {
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 9px 14px;
      min-height: 42px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease, background .15s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover:not(:disabled) { background: var(--surface-2); box-shadow: 0 5px 14px rgba(23,32,51,.08); }
    .btn:active:not(:disabled) { transform: translateY(1px); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--blue); color: #fff; border-color: var(--blue); }
    .btn-primary:hover:not(:disabled) { background: #1e548f; }
    .btn-danger { color: var(--red); border-color: #f1b7b2; background: #fff; }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; border-color: transparent; color: var(--muted); }
    .btn-small { min-height: 34px; padding: 6px 10px; font-size: 12px; }
    .choice-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
    .choice {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 13px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 11px;
      background: var(--surface-2);
    }
    .choice input { margin-top: 3px; accent-color: var(--blue); }
    .choice-copy strong { display: block; font-size: 13px; }
    .choice-copy span { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 2px; }
    .upload-zone {
      border: 1.5px dashed #aebdce;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px;
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--surface-2);
      transition: border-color .15s ease, background .15s ease;
    }
    .upload-zone.dragover { border-color: var(--blue); background: var(--blue-soft); }
    .upload-zone .upload-icon {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      margin: 0 auto 10px;
      border-radius: 13px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .upload-zone p { margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 750; }
    .upload-zone small { color: var(--muted); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .file-list { display: grid; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
    .file-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
      gap: 11px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .file-type {
      min-width: 42px;
      padding: 5px 6px;
      border-radius: 7px;
      background: var(--blue-soft);
      color: var(--blue);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 850;
    }
    .file-name { overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }
    .file-meta { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; }
    .file-remove { border: 0; background: transparent; color: var(--muted); padding: 5px 7px; border-radius: 7px; }
    .file-remove:hover { color: var(--red); background: var(--red-soft); }
    .validation { margin-top: 12px; color: var(--red); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 650; }
    .consent {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--surface-2);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .consent input { margin-top: 4px; accent-color: var(--blue); }
    .consent label { font-weight: 500; }
    .actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }
    .api-state { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .api-state::before { content: ""; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #98a2b3; }
    .api-state.ok { color: var(--green); }
    .api-state.ok::before { background: var(--green); }
    .api-state.bad { color: var(--red); }
    .api-state.bad::before { background: var(--red); }

    /* process */
    .process-shell { width: min(900px, 100%); margin: 0 auto; }
    .process-hero { text-align: center; padding: 14px 0 26px; }
    .process-orbit {
      width: 92px;
      height: 92px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
    }
    .process-orbit::before, .process-orbit::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
    }
    .process-orbit::before { inset: 0; border-top-color: var(--blue); border-right-color: var(--blue); animation: spin 1.4s linear infinite; }
    .process-orbit::after { inset: 13px; border-bottom-color: #6aa9e8; animation: spinReverse 1s linear infinite; }
    .process-core { width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--navy); color: #fff; display: grid; place-items: center; font-weight: 800; }
    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
    @keyframes spinReverse { to { transform: rotate(-360deg); } }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .process-orbit::before, .process-orbit::after { animation: none; } }
    .progress-track { height: 9px; background: #e9eef5; border-radius: 999px; overflow: hidden; }
    .progress-bar { height: 100%; width: 0; border-radius: inherit; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), #61a6e8); transition: width .35s ease; }
    .progress-meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .process-list { display: grid; gap: 9px; margin-top: 24px; }
    .process-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 26px 1fr auto;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 13px 14px;
      border-radius: 11px;
      background: var(--surface-2);
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .process-item.active { background: var(--blue-soft); border-color: #b8d3ef; color: var(--ink); }
    .process-item.done { color: var(--green); }
    .process-icon { width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; }
    .process-item.active .process-icon { background: var(--blue); color: #fff; border-color: var(--blue); }
    .process-item.done .process-icon { background: var(--green-soft); color: var(--green); border-color: #9ed2c0; }
    .process-item strong { display: block; font-size: 13px; color: inherit; }
    .process-item span { font-size: 11px; }
    .agent-board { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr)); gap:10px; margin-top:16px; }
    .agent-flow-label { grid-column:1 / -1; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; }
    .agent-flow-label strong { color:var(--ink); font-size:12px; }
    .agent-card { border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:13px; padding:12px; background:var(--surface); min-height:88px; }
    .agent-card.active { border-color:#8bb8e7; background:var(--blue-soft); }
    .agent-card.done { border-color:#9ed2c0; background:var(--green-soft); }
    .agent-card.error { border-color:#f2a7a0; background:var(--red-soft); }
    .agent-card-head { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:8px; }
    .agent-card strong { font-size:13px; }
    .agent-card p { margin:8px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; }
    .agent-summary { white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; }
    .agent-card.active .agent-summary { color:var(--ink); }
    .agent-state { font-size:10px; font-weight:800; color:var(--muted); }
    .agent-card.active .agent-state { color:var(--blue); }
    .agent-card.done .agent-state { color:var(--green); }
    .agent-trace { display:grid; gap:10px; }
    .agent-trace-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:180px minmax(0,1fr) 110px; gap:12px; align-items:start; padding:12px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
    .agent-trace-row:last-child { border-bottom:0; }
    .agent-trace-summary { white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; }
    .process-error { margin-top: 18px; padding: 16px; border-radius: 11px; background: var(--red-soft); border: 1px solid #f1b7b2; color: #7a1b14; }
    .process-error strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .diagnostic-summary { display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .diagnostic-status { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; border-radius: 999px; padding: 4px 9px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #edaaa4; color: var(--red); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; }
    .diagnostic-title { font-weight: 800; color: #7a1b14; }
    .diagnostic-advice { margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 9px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.6); color: #6f271f; font-size: 12px; }
    .diagnostic-details { margin-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #edaaa4; padding-top: 12px; }
    .diagnostic-details summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 800; color: #7a1b14; }
    .diagnostic-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 8px; margin-top: 11px; }
    .diagnostic-field { padding: 9px 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.7); min-width: 0; }
    .diagnostic-field span { display: block; color: #9b4a42; font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .diagnostic-field code { display: block; color: #5d211b; font-size: 11px; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: anywhere; }
    .diagnostic-code { margin: 11px 0 0; padding: 12px; border-radius: 9px; background: #371815; color: #ffe9e6; font: 11px/1.55 ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: anywhere; max-height: 260px; overflow-y: auto; }
    .diagnostic-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px; }
    .probe-result { margin-top: 12px; padding: 11px 12px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--line); background: var(--surface-2); font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }
    .probe-result.ok { border-color: #a8d7c7; background: var(--green-soft); color: var(--green); }
    .probe-result.bad { border-color: #f1b7b2; background: var(--red-soft); color: var(--red); }

    /* output */
    .output-toolbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .output-title { margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .output-meta { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .toolbar-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 8px; }
    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .tab-button {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      border: 0;
      border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 11px 14px 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .tab-button.active { color: var(--blue); border-bottom-color: var(--blue); }
    .tab-panel { display: none; }
    .tab-panel.active { display: block; }
    .kpi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .kpi { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; }
    .kpi-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .kpi-value { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -.04em; margin-top: 3px; }
    .kpi-value.red { color: var(--red); }
    .kpi-value.amber { color: var(--amber); }
    .dashboard-chart-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .dashboard-chart { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; min-width: 0; }
    .dashboard-chart-head { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; margin-bottom:13px; }
    .dashboard-chart-head h2 { margin:0; font-size:14px; }
    .dashboard-chart-head span { color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; }
    .chart-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:76px minmax(0,1fr) 28px; align-items:center; gap:9px; font-size:11px; }
    .chart-row + .chart-row { margin-top:9px; }
    .chart-label { color:var(--muted); white-space:nowrap; }
    .chart-track { height:9px; border-radius:999px; background:var(--surface-2); overflow:hidden; }
    .chart-fill { height:100%; border-radius:inherit; background:#31b7c3; }
    .chart-fill.critical, .chart-fill.miss { background:#ff6b6b; }
    .chart-fill.action, .chart-fill.partial { background:#e2b400; }
    .chart-fill.advisory { background:#3478d4; }
    .chart-fill.watch, .chart-fill.complete { background:#2eaa7b; }
    .chart-fill.unclear { background:#e2b400; }
    .chart-count { text-align:right; font-weight:800; font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums; }
    .overview-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.25fr .75fr; gap: 20px; }
    .fact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--line); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
    .fact { background: #fff; padding: 13px 14px; min-height: 78px; }
    .fact-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .fact-value { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-word; }
    .summary-block + .summary-block { margin-top: 18px; }
    .summary-block h3 { color: var(--navy); }
    .summary-block p { margin-bottom: 0; color: #344054; }
    .bullet-list { margin: 7px 0 0; padding-left: 19px; color: #344054; }
    .bullet-list li + li { margin-top: 5px; }
    .flow { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 24px; align-items: stretch; }
    .flow-item { position: relative; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; background: var(--surface-2); padding: 14px; min-height: 112px; }
    .flow-item:not(:last-child)::after { content: "→"; position: absolute; right: -19px; top: 42%; color: var(--blue); font-weight: 900; }
    .flow-label { color: var(--blue); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .flow-text { font-size: 12px; color: #344054; }
    .section-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(20,55,95,.05); }
    .section-card + .section-card { margin-top: 16px; }
    .section-card-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .section-card-head h2 { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .filters { display: flex; align-items: end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 9px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .filters .field { min-width: 160px; flex: 1 1 180px; }
    .filters input, .filters select { min-height: 38px; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 12px; }
    .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
    th { text-align: left; color: var(--muted); background: var(--surface-2); padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); white-space: nowrap; }
    td { padding: 11px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); vertical-align: top; min-width: 92px; }
    td.wide { min-width: 210px; }
    tbody tr:hover { background: #fafbfd; }
    .tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; border-radius: 999px; padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; white-space: nowrap; border: 1px solid transparent; }
    .tag-critical, .tag-miss, .tag-delay { color: var(--red); background: var(--red-soft); border-color: #f4beb9; }
    .tag-action, .tag-partial, .tag-change, .tag-unclear { color: #765b00; background: #fff7cc; border-color: #ead36a; }
    .tag-advisory { color: #1959a6; background: #e8f2ff; border-color: #b8d3f4; }
    .tag-watch, .tag-done, .tag-exceed { color: var(--green); background: var(--green-soft); border-color: #b6dfd1; }
    .tag-neutral { color: var(--muted); background: #eef2f6; border-color: #d9e1ea; }
    .metric-list { display: grid; gap: 11px; }
    .metric-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(190px, .9fr) minmax(260px, 1.4fr) auto; gap: 16px; align-items: center; padding: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; }
    .metric-row.metric-urgent { border-left:5px solid var(--red); background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red-soft),var(--surface) 18%); }
    .metric-row.metric-review { border-left:5px solid #d9ad00; background:linear-gradient(90deg,#fff9dc,var(--surface) 18%); }
    .metric-row.metric-info { border-left:5px solid #3478d4; }
    .metric-row.metric-normal { border-left:5px solid var(--green); }
    .metric-name { font-weight: 750; font-size: 13px; }
    .metric-sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; }
    .metric-values { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:8px; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .metric-value-box { min-width:0; padding:8px 10px; border-radius:9px; background:var(--surface-2); border:1px solid var(--line); }
    .metric-value-box span { display:block; margin-bottom:2px; color:var(--muted); font-size:10px; }
    .metric-value-box strong { display:block; color:var(--ink); font-size:13px; font-weight:800; overflow-wrap:anywhere; }
    .metric-value-box.actual { border-color:#b8d3f4; background:#f2f7ff; }
    .comparison-key-value { color:var(--ink); font-weight:800; }
    tbody tr.comparison-urgent { background:var(--red-soft); }
    tbody tr.comparison-review { background:#fff9dc; }
    tbody tr.comparison-info { background:#f2f7ff; }
    tbody tr.comparison-normal { background:#f1faf6; }
    .metric-state-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin: 7px 0 6px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); }
    .metric-state-row strong { color: var(--text); font-size: 11px; }
    .bar-track { height: 9px; border-radius: 999px; background: #e9eef5; overflow: hidden; }
    .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: inherit; min-width: 0; }
    .bar-fill.bar-achieved { background: var(--green); }
    .bar-fill.bar-partial { background: #d9ad00; }
    .bar-fill.bar-missed { background: var(--red); }
    .bar-fill.bar-pending, .bar-fill.bar-unclear { background: #d9ad00; }
    .metric-legend { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; }
    .metric-legend span { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; white-space:nowrap; }
    .metric-legend i { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; display:inline-block; }
    .metric-legend .urgent { background:var(--red); }
    .metric-legend .review { background:#d9ad00; }
    .metric-legend .normal { background:linear-gradient(90deg,#3478d4 0 50%,var(--green) 50%); }
    .risk-list { display: grid; gap: 10px; }
    .risk-card { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: 13px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; }
    .risk-card.risk-critical { border-left: 5px solid var(--red); }
    .risk-card.risk-action { border-left: 5px solid #d9ad00; }
    .risk-card.risk-advisory { border-left: 5px solid #3478d4; }
    .risk-card.risk-watch { border-left: 5px solid var(--green); }
    .risk-body h3 { margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .risk-problem { color: #344054; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 13px; }
    .risk-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 9px; }
    .risk-fact { background: var(--surface-2); border-radius: 9px; padding: 10px; }
    .risk-fact span { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .risk-fact strong { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 650; }
    .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 24px; }
    .timeline::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 8px; bottom: 8px; left: 7px; width: 2px; background: var(--line); }
    .timeline-item { position: relative; padding: 0 0 18px 16px; }
    .timeline-item::before { content: ""; position: absolute; left: -22px; top: 6px; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--blue-soft); }
    .timeline-period { color: var(--blue); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; }
    .timeline-title { font-weight: 750; margin: 2px 0 4px; }
    .timeline-copy { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .empty { padding: 28px; text-align: center; color: var(--muted); border: 1px dashed #c7d2df; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--surface-2); }
    .source-list { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
    .source-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(150px,.8fr) 90px 1fr; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); font-size: 12px; }
    .source-doc { font-weight: 750; }
    .source-loc { color: var(--blue); }
    .limitation { padding: 12px 14px; background: var(--amber-soft); border: 1px solid #f0d3a2; border-radius: 10px; color: #6f4305; font-size: 12px; }
    .limitation + .limitation { margin-top: 8px; }
    .preflight { margin-top:14px; display:grid; gap:8px; }
    .preflight-item { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:9px; padding:10px 12px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; background:var(--surface-2); color:#344054; font-size:12px; }
    .preflight-item.warn { border-color:#e8c46c; background:#fff9e8; color:#6f4b00; }
    .preflight-item.block { border-color:#f0aaa4; background:var(--red-soft); color:#8f2118; }
    .file-profile { display:grid; grid-template-columns:minmax(140px,1fr) minmax(110px,.65fr); gap:7px; margin-top:7px; }
    .file-profile select, .file-profile input { min-height:34px; padding:5px 8px; font-size:11px; }
    .baseline-banner { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:space-between; gap:16px; margin:0 0 16px; padding:14px 16px; border:1px solid #e8c46c; border-left:5px solid #d9ad00; border-radius:12px; background:#fff9e8; }
    .baseline-banner.confirmed { border-color:#abd9c8; border-left-color:var(--green); background:var(--green-soft); }
    .baseline-banner strong { display:block; margin-bottom:2px; }
    .validation-summary { margin:0 0 16px; padding:12px 14px; border:1px solid #b8d3f4; border-radius:11px; background:#eef6ff; color:#174f8c; font-size:12px; }
    .action-grid { display:grid; gap:10px; }
    .action-card { display:grid; grid-template-columns:auto minmax(180px,1fr) minmax(130px,.5fr) minmax(130px,.5fr); gap:12px; align-items:start; padding:14px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
    .action-card input, .action-card select, .action-card textarea { width:100%; min-height:36px; padding:7px 9px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px; background:#fff; font-size:11px; }
    .action-card textarea { min-height:58px; resize:vertical; }
    .consensus-table td:first-child { font-weight:750; min-width:170px; }
    .decision { display:inline-flex; border-radius:999px; padding:3px 8px; font-size:10px; font-weight:800; color:#0e6d51; background:var(--green-soft); border:1px solid #b6dfd1; }
    .evidence-link { border:1px solid #b8d3f4; border-radius:999px; padding:2px 7px; background:#eef6ff; color:#1959a6; font-size:10px; font-weight:750; }
    .evidence-target { scroll-margin-top:20px; }
    .evidence-target:target { background:#fff7cc; outline:3px solid rgba(217,173,0,.25); }
    .print-only { display:none; }

    /* 밝은 업무용 결과 화면 */
    #view-output { background:#f8fbff; border:1px solid #d7e2ef; border-radius:20px; padding:22px; box-shadow:0 18px 50px rgba(20,55,95,.08); }
    #view-output .kpi { background:linear-gradient(145deg,#ffffff,#f1f7ff); border-color:#cfdded; box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(32,74,120,.06); }
    #view-output .kpi-value { color:#1857a6; }
    #view-output .kpi-value.red { color:#c62828; }
    #view-output .kpi-value.amber { color:#9a6700; }
    #view-output .dashboard-chart { box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(32,74,120,.05); }
    #view-output .section-card { box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(32,74,120,.05); }
    #view-output .tab-button.active { color:#1857a6; border-bottom-color:#1857a6; }
    .summary-block.is-primary { background:#eef5ff; border-left:4px solid #2669b5; border-radius:10px; padding:13px 14px; }
    .summary-block.is-primary h3 { color:#1857a6; }
    .inline-emphasis { display:inline; padding:1px 4px; border-radius:5px; background:#fff0d6; color:#7a4c00; font-weight:800; box-decoration-break:clone; -webkit-box-decoration-break:clone; }
    .inline-emphasis.danger { background:#ffebe9; color:#a82318; }
    .inline-emphasis.info { background:#e8f2ff; color:#1959a6; }
    .inline-emphasis.good { background:#e8f6f0; color:#0e6d51; }
    .key-number { color:#1857a6; font-weight:850; }
    footer { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 40px)); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 0 30px; text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .grid-2, .overview-grid, .intro-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .dashboard-chart-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 9px; }
      .flow-item { min-height: auto; }
      .flow-item:not(:last-child)::after { content: "↓"; right: auto; left: 50%; top: auto; bottom: -17px; }
      .metric-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; }
      .risk-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .topbar-inner, main, footer { width: calc(100% - 24px); }
      .topbar-inner { min-height: 66px; }
      .brand-sub, .session-badge span:last-child { display: none; }
      .brand-logo { width:210px; max-width:58vw; }
      .brand > div:last-child { display:none; }
      .intro-copy { padding:22px; }
      .workflow-inner { width: calc(100% - 24px); }
      .workflow-step { font-size: 11px; }
      .workflow-step > span:last-child { display: none; }
      main { padding-top: 24px; }
      .card { padding: 18px; }
      .grid-3, .choice-grid, .fact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .output-toolbar { flex-direction: column; }
      .toolbar-actions { justify-content: flex-start; }
      .source-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2px; }
      .input-with-action { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .diagnostic-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .file-profile, .action-card { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .agent-board { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
      .agent-trace-row { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      #view-output { padding:14px; border-radius:14px; }
    }
    @media print {
      @page { margin: 14mm 12mm 20mm; }
      body { background: #fff; font-size: 11px; }
      .topbar, .workflow, #view-input, #view-process, .toolbar-actions, .tabs, .filters, footer { display: none !important; }
      .print-only { display:block !important; }
      .print-header { padding:0 0 10px; margin-bottom:14px; border-bottom:2px solid #172033; font-weight:750; }
      .print-footer { position:fixed; left:0; right:0; bottom:0; padding:7px 0; border-top:1px solid #98a2b3; background:#fff; text-align:center; font-size:9px; }
      main { width: 100%; padding: 0; }
      #view-output { display: block !important; }
      .tab-panel { display: block !important; margin-bottom: 18px; }
      .section-card, .kpi { box-shadow: none; }
      .kpi, .risk-card, .metric-row, tr { break-inside: avoid; }
      #view-output { --surface:#fff; --surface-2:#f7f9fc; --ink:#172033; --muted:#667085; --line:#dce3ed; background:#fff; color:#172033; border:0; padding:0; }
      #view-output .output-title, #view-output h2, #view-output h3, #view-output td, #view-output .fact-value { color:#172033; }
      #view-output .summary-block p, #view-output .bullet-list, #view-output .flow-text, #view-output .risk-problem, #view-output .timeline-copy { color:#344054; }
      #view-output .kpi, #view-output .dashboard-chart, #view-output .section-card, #view-output .fact, #view-output th, #view-output .risk-fact, #view-output .flow-item { background:#fff; color:#172033; border-color:#dce3ed; }
      #view-output .kpi-label, #view-output .output-meta, #view-output .helper, #view-output .metric-sub, #view-output .fact-label, #view-output .chart-label { color:#667085; }
      #view-output .kpi-value, #view-output .kpi-value.red, #view-output .kpi-value.amber { color:#172033; }
      .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); }
      table { font-size: 9px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="topbar-inner">
        <div class="brand">
          <img class="brand-logo" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="IITP 정보통신기획평가원">
          <div>
            <div class="brand-title">R&amp;D Review Studio</div>
            <div class="brand-sub">연구개발계획 대비 수행실적 분석</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="session-badge" id="sessionBadge">
          <span class="session-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span id="sessionLabel">API 연결 전</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="workflow" aria-label="분석 단계">
      <div class="workflow-inner">
        <div class="workflow-step active" data-workflow="input"><span class="step-number">1</span><span>INPUT · 분석 설정</span></div>
        <div class="workflow-step" data-workflow="process"><span class="step-number">2</span><span>PROCESS · AI 분석</span></div>
        <div class="workflow-step" data-workflow="output"><span class="step-number">3</span><span>OUTPUT · 검토 결과</span></div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <section id="view-input">
        <div class="intro-hero">
          <div class="intro-copy">
            <div class="eyebrow">IITP R&amp;D Review Assistant</div>
            <h1>연구개발계획과 수행실적의 변동을 한눈에 확인하세요</h1>
            <p>연구개발계획서를 기준으로 단계보고서·최종보고서의 정량적 목표, 정성적 목표, 일정, 산출물과 기관별 역할이 어떻게 달라졌는지 분석하는 내부 검토 지원 도구입니다. 문서에서 확인된 근거만 사용하며 공식 평가나 최종 판단을 대신하지 않습니다.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="intro-flow" aria-label="사용 흐름">
            <div class="intro-step"><span class="intro-step-number">1</span><div><strong>기준 계획서 등록</strong><span>승인된 연구개발계획서를 선택합니다.</span></div></div>
            <div class="intro-step"><span class="intro-step-number">2</span><div><strong>비교 보고서 추가</strong><span>단계·최종보고서 또는 진도자료를 추가합니다.</span></div></div>
            <div class="intro-step"><span class="intro-step-number">3</span><div><strong>변동·위험 확인</strong><span>목표, 일정, 증빙과 확인 질문을 검토합니다.</span></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="intro-note"><span class="intro-chip">특정 사업에 종속되지 않음</span><span class="intro-chip">정량·정성 목표 비교</span><span class="intro-chip">원문 근거 표시</span><span class="intro-chip">개인정보 출력 제외</span></div>
        </div>

        <form id="analysisForm" novalidate>
          <div class="grid-2">
            <section class="card">
              <div class="card-head">
                <div class="head-copy">
                  <div class="section-number">01</div>
                  <div><h2>API 연결</h2><p>브라우저에서 OpenAI Responses API를 직접 호출합니다.</p></div>
                </div>
                <span class="api-state" id="apiState">연결 확인 전</span>
              </div>

              <div class="notice">
                <span class="notice-icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
                <div><strong>로컬·개인 테스트 전용 구성</strong><br>별도 백엔드 없이 동작하므로 브라우저에 입력한 키를 완전히 보호할 수 없습니다. 키와 문서는 저장하지 않으며 현재 페이지 메모리에서만 사용합니다. 운영 배포용으로는 권장되지 않습니다.</div>
              </div>

              <div class="field">
                <label for="apiKey">OpenAI API Key</label>
                <div class="input-with-action">
                  <input id="apiKey" type="password" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" placeholder="sk-…" aria-describedby="apiKeyHelp">
                  <button class="btn" type="button" id="toggleKey">표시</button>
                </div>
                <small id="apiKeyHelp">HTML, 로컬 저장소, 세션 저장소에 기록하지 않습니다.</small>
              </div>

              <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:16px">
                <div class="field">
                  <label for="modelSelect">GPT-5 모델</label>
                  <select id="modelSelect">
                    <option value="gpt-5.6">GPT-5.6 (권장)</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5.6-sol">GPT-5.6 Sol</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5.6-terra">GPT-5.6 Terra</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5.6-luna">GPT-5.6 Luna</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5.5">GPT-5.5</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5.4">GPT-5.4</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5.2">GPT-5.2</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5.1">GPT-5.1</option>
                    <option value="gpt-5">GPT-5</option>
                  </select>
                  <small>연결 확인 시 계정에서 사용 가능한 GPT-5 계열 모델로 갱신합니다.</small>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                  <label for="reasoningEffort">추론 강도</label>
                  <select id="reasoningEffort">
                    <option value="low">낮음 · 빠른 검토</option>
                    <option value="medium" selected>중간 · 균형</option>
                    <option value="high">높음 · 정밀 검토</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>

